Utterance.UttText: Nina Maria Carey, 67 under Dr Jaime, came in with bronchitis, fever and cough.
She is just newly diagnosed to have cancer.
So aggressive that it had spread to her lungs.
Her husband needs to be informed as well as her 4 children.

We can ask her if she wants some counselling and also if she and her family needs to talk with the doctors about her her treatment plan and all information about her cancer. her obs are all stable. afebrile. she is self caring and on general diet. nil other complaints raised.

Phrase.PhraseText: on general diet. nil other complaints
